dget availability, internal salary equityconsiderations, and available market information.Please include the following documents with your application:* Resume* Cover Letter* Two Professional ReferencesThe University of Denver is committed to enhancing the diversity of itsfaculty and staff. We are an Equal Opportunity/Affirmative Action Employer.All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment regardlessof age, race, color, national origin, religion, sex, sexualorientation, gender identity, disability, military/ veteran status orany other status protected by law.All offers of employment are based upon satisfactory completion of a criminalhistory background check.Advertised: April 17, 2020Applications close: ", 
